	   <tr><td colspan=2>The effect is still very useful, as are the stats. If you're a ranger/rogue, or a monk with a CoF, you're already going to reach the haste cap, so an item like an rbb in your belt slot is a waste.<br><br>The stats on this are BETTER than the RBB (if you have a higher haste item), due to the 30 hp. 30 hp &gt; 10 stamina. You may look at it as just 30 hp, but every little bit of HP helps. I *love* this belt, I already have my epics, and ditched my RBB and replaced it with this item; couldn't be happier.<br><br><br>Menthas Mynt Leaf <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
